01:00:01.290 --> 01:00:04.210
That's related to a
complicated issue which

01:00:04.210 --> 01:00:05.990
goes by the name of confinement.

01:00:05.990 --> 01:00:08.940
Although the gluon is
massless, it's confined.

01:00:08.940 --> 01:00:11.820
And confined means that
it cannot exist as a free

01:00:11.820 --> 01:00:13.260
particle.

01:00:13.260 --> 01:00:14.960
In some sense, the
strong interactions

01:00:14.960 --> 01:00:18.670
